pl.edu.mimuw.changeanalyzer.models

Class DataSetBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.mimuw.changeanalyzer.models.DataSetBuilder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChunkDataSetBuilder

    public abstract class DataSetBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract base class for data set builders - classes tranforming method histories into model instances. Each builder class defines a set of attributes and provides methods to produce instances with this attributes. Created instaces may represent commits, groups of commits, method snapshots, etc. depending on the model used by a concrete builder.
    Author:
    Adam Wierzbicki
